{
  "stem": "9156.9",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was very sick, and he would come with a nurse, and say, my goodness, you're building up this place.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anybody who wants to see this place has to know that there isn't a light fixture; there isn't a porch that isn't done by Paul's hands.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He laid the roof.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He mixed the cement for every step.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I'm not going into that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that's why the house means a lot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But that's not only why I tell that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because, from the moment we had this place we said it's also a refuge for people, because there were so many people who had suffered so terribly.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they came here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I could name one after another who has stayed in this place, not for a few days, but for weeks, for months, and for years.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There's one-- oh, dear.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I-- his-- I knew him as Rauschenplat, but he was, later, the-- responsible for all the Western Germany radio.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But he had been an underground worker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he stayed here, when the house did not look like it looks today.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But he was-- he could be-- he had a decent place.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He had-- people were kind, and so on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I think that's very important to remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Juergen Ziegler, whose father was killed by the Nazis, was with us for almost three years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We got him through graduate school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I know people say we didn't have children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That's true.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "In all that period, we couldn't have children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And when Paul went into the army, we tried, and it didn't work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But we had a lot of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We had a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "This house has been-- Paul always said, everybody but George Washington slept here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So it was that way.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
